registry
Class ComponentRegistry

java.lang.Object
  registry.ComponentRegistry

public class ComponentRegistry
extends Object

A registry class for various components in Overherd. When a class is created it links itself to the corresponding registry object so it can be accessed from any class.

kevin nam
